item.title: CVE-2017-20125|2024-08-05T21:45:25.974Z -- unspecified -- online%20hotel%20booking%20system%20pro
item.description: A vulnerability classified as critical was found in Online Hotel Booking System Pro 1.2. Affected by this vulnerability is an unknown functionality of the file /roomtype-details.php. The manipulation of the argument tid leads to sql injection. The attack can be launched remotely. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used.
